Replaced DocumentsView with TopicBrowserView - new two-panel knowledge browser with topic sidebar and content area.

Implementation:
- Added Topic model (id, title, description, icon, linkedProjectId, autoCreated, timestamps)
- Updated AgentDocument and ResearchRequest models to include topicId FK
- Created TopicBrowserView with:
  * Topic sidebar: search, unread counts, icons, create new topic button
  * Content area: documents grouped by type, research requests with status, action buttons
  * Expandable sections for documents and requests
  * Document detail view with markdown rendering
  * Create topic and research request sheets
- Added API methods: loadTopics(), createTopic(), createResearchRequestForTopic()
- Updated AppViewModel with topics array and loadTopics() method
- Replaced DocumentsView with TopicBrowserView in MainView
- Uses Theme.swift colors throughout (cardBg, subtle, accent, etc.)

Build: Successful (warnings only - deprecated onChange API)
Tests: Manual testing required - UI component (Swift UI Preview available)
